To activate the control panel feature, you will need to install the [user](https://github.com/mecha-cms/x.user "User") extension as the generic log-in/out system.

![Panel](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1669261/104103529-31af0f00-52d5-11eb-8e08-fe2c4f2d3b4c.png)

### Usage

 - Make sure you have uploaded the required extensions.
 - Upload the `panel` folder to `.\lot\x` folder.
 - Now visit your site! You should be redirected to create a new user.